data.description: Welcome to this tranquil oasis! This stunning property boasts over 5 acres of serene countryside complete w/ a meticulously maintained irrigated pasture and small apple orchard making it a haven for all outdoor enthusiasts. This spacious estate highlights fresh paint both inside and out showcasing a cozy covered front porch, vaulted ceilings, new laminate floors, and brand new plush carpets throughout. The property features a generously sized main suite large enough to accommodate an office, a soaker tub, and walk-in rain shower. With a covered pergola patio, raised garden beds, and various mature trees on the property, this is your own private sanctuary! On the side of the well-insulated shop, 4 stables are featured offering endless possibilities and a haven for horse lovers. Included in the shop is an elevator to effortlessly transport items to the loft. With solar panels in place you can enjoy a lower power bill while being eco conscious. Under 10mins from i84 and 5 mins to Purple Sage Golf Course.
